="fm-vol-iss-date">Published online 2005 Oct 18. </span>  <span class="doi">doi:\xc2\xa0<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1186%2F1471-2334-5-87" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1276795&amp;issue-id=354737&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CFront%20Matter&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">10.1186/1471-2334-5-87</a></span></div></div></div><div class="inline_block four_col va_top show-overflow align_right"><div class="fm-citation-ids"><div class="fm-citation-pmcid"><span class="fm-citation-ids-label">PMCID: </span><span>PMC1276795</span></div><div class="fm-citation-pmid">PMID: <a href="/pubmed/16229749">16229749</a></div></div></div></div><h1 class="content-title">A simple and rapid approach for screening of SARS-coronavirus genotypes: an evaluation study</h1><div class="half_rhythm"><div class="contrib-group fm-author"><a href="/pubmed/?term=Chung%20GT%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=16229749" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139686481633200" co-class="co-affbox">Grace TY Chung</a>,<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Chiu%20RW%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=16229749" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139686473480816" co-class="co-affbox">Rossa WK Chiu</a>,<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Cheung%20JL%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=16229749" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139686481273328" co-class="co-affbox">Jo LK Cheung</a>,<sup>3</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Jin%20Y%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=16229749" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139686481271072" co-class="co-affbox">Yongjie Jin</a>,<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Chim%20SS%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=16229749" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139686551915888" co-class="co-affbox">Stephen SC Chim</a>,<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Chan%20PK%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=16229749" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm139686555255808" co-class=